   Schema: Associative_text_arm  Entity: Annotation_curve  
   <express_ref linkend="associative_text:arm:Associative_text_arm.Annotation_curve"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Associative_text_arm.Annotation_curve">An <b>Annotation_curve</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="associative_text:arm:Associative_text_arm.Annotation_element"/>  two-dimensional trimmed curve that is used to annotate a drawing or a geometric model.
</ext_description>
<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Associative_text_arm  Entity: Annotation_curve  Attribute: annotation_curve_type 
   <express_ref linkend="associative_text:arm:Associative_text_arm.Annotation_curve.annotation_curve_type"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Associative_text_arm.Annotation_curve.annotation_curve_type">
<p>the kind of <b>Annotation_curve</b>. This information is provided with respect to the intended usage of the annotated object.</p> <example>'text leader' is an example for <b>annotation_curve_type</b>.</example> <p>The value of this attribute need not be specified.</p>
</ext_description>
<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Associative_text_arm  Entity: Annotation_element  
   <express_ref linkend="associative_text:arm:Associative_text_arm.Annotation_element"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Associative_text_arm.Annotation_element">
An <b>Annotation_element</b> is a type of  <express_ref linkend="appearance_assignment:arm:Appearance_assignment_arm.Styled_element"/>
 that is a representation of an annotation.</ext_description>

